ên hiểu giốc - Chiết hoa - 霜天曉角－折花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-Ti%E1%BB%87p/author-aBhZ-WX7vBdkSnC7TRFytA">Tưởng Tiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-T%E1%BB%91ng-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-M%E1%BA%ADu-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-khanh-s%E1%BB%A9-L%E1%BB%97/poem-ouFCraEXy-Xfn56f4fUkOw">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - Tống Chương Đức Mậu Đại khanh sứ Lỗ - 水調歌頭—送章德茂大卿使虜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-hKnlT065602cE5xw0UFbWA">Trần Lượng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/Th%E1%BB%ABa-gi%C3%A1o-ho%E1%BA%A1-nh%E1%BB%8B-gi%C3%A1p-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%81n-thi/poem-Iw-1wa6Dz53m7ME0wyrZ3g">Thừa giáo hoạ nhị giáp Nguyễn Thượng Hiền thi - 承教和二甲進士阮尚賢詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Khu%C3%AA/author-VbN3Sg3IlecAJHEAqRJ56A">Dương Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-%E1%BB%B6-Trang/Tr%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-MVyeRKP-52SSd2X8KrodfQ">Trí tửu - 置酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-%E1%BB%B6-Trang/author-4yq3urVCwQJBS8lqbgoHQw">Lưu Ỷ Trang</a>)<br></div>	</div>
